narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Excellent course on the mathematics of complex systems, covering all the bases. I would definitely recommend with course, with the caveat to make sure you attend office hours and get to know the professor a little bit. He is an affable guy, but this didn't completely come across in lecture.
